OL,3,CPedestrian killed by truck was the
OL,4,C'kindest man you would meet'
OL,6,FA man who died following a crash in
OL,7,FNewcastle has been described as the
OL,8,F"kindest person you would meet."
OL,10,FCraig Andrew Russell, from Newcastle,
OL,11,Fdied at the scene of the collision on
OL,12,FCradlewell Bypass in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Tuesday 22 October.
OL,15,FThe 50-year-old pedestrian was struck
OL,16,Fby a blue and red Volvo articulated
OL,17,Ftruck.
