OL,3,CPedestrian killed by truck was the
OL,4,C'kindest man you would meet'
OL,6,FPaying tribute to him in a statement,
OL,7,Fhis family said his death had left a
OL,8,F"massive hole" in the hearts of those
OL,9,Fwho loved them.
OL,11,FThey said: "Craig, as everybody knows
OL,12,Fhad his ups and downs in life, but he
OL,13,Fwas always the kindest person you
OL,14,Fwould meet, he would do anything for
OL,15,Fanyone and was always polite and
OL,16,Fextremely grateful.
OL,18,F"Craig couldn't pass you in the street
OL,19,Fwithout stopping, saying hello and
OL,20,Fasking how you were.
