OL,3,CPedestrian killed by truck was the
OL,4,C'kindest man you would meet'
OL,6,F"Craig, around a year ago, got a dog.
OL,7,FCraig loved that dog so much and was
OL,8,Fnever without Bear Bear, people would
OL,9,Fnotice the dog before Craig.
OL,11,F"Whenever Bear Bear got away, he was
OL,12,Fwidely known he was Craig's dog and
OL,13,Fwas easily returned to him.
OL,15,F"Craig also loved his family so much,
OL,16,Fand was never shy to tell them how
OL,17,Fmuch he loved them or how he was
OL,18,Ffeeling.
