OL,4,C'kindest man you would meet'
OL,6,F"Craig's unexpected and sudden passing
OL,7,Fhas left a massive hole in the hearts
OL,8,Fof those that loved him, that will
OL,9,Fnever be filled. How does life go on
OL,10,Fwithout you?
OL,12,F"Mam Lillian, Dad Colin, Brother
OL,13,FAaron, sister Kelda, Nephew Robert and
OL,14,Fthe rest of the family will forever
OL,15,Fmiss you, sleep tight.
OL,17,F"Forever the blue-eyed boy, forever
OL,18,F50."
