OL,3,CPedestrian killed by truck was the
OL,4,C'kindest man you would meet'
OL,6,FThe collision happened on the A1058
OL,7,FCoast Road, between the Corner House
OL,8,Fand Cradlewell, at about 1:15 am on 22
OL,9,FOctober.
OL,11,FFor reasons yet to be established, it
OL,12,Fwas reported that a Volvo articulated
OL,13,Ftruck had collided with a pedestrian.
OL,15,FA man in his 60s was arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of causing death by careless
OL,17,Fdriving and remains on police bail
OL,18,Fwhile the investigation continues.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
