OL,6,FOfficers continue to appeal for
OL,7,Fwitnesses or anyone with dashcam
OL,8,Ffootage of the moments leading up to
OL,9,Fthe collision to get in touch.
OL,11,FSergeant John Sanderson, of
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police's Serious Collision
OL,13,FInvestigation Unit, said: "All of our
OL,14,Fthoughts continue to be with Craig's
OL,15,Floved one at this incredibly difficult
OL,16,Ftime, and we will support his family
OL,17,Fin any way we can.
